Vladimir Vladimirovich Putin  (bɔn 7 Ɔktoba 1952) na wan Rɔshian pɔlitiksman ɛn fɔma intɛlijɛns ɔfisa we dɔn wok as di prɛsidɛnt fɔ Rɔshia frɔm 2012, i bin dɔn wok bifo bitwin 2000 ɛn 2008.I bin bi di praymɛnt minista na Rɔshia frɔm 1999 to 2000 ɛn bak frɔm 2008 to 2012, so i dɔn kɔntinyu fɔ wok as prɛsidɛnt ɔ praymɛnt minista frɔm 1999 go bifo.

Putin bin wok as KGB fɔrin intɛlijɛns ɔfisa fɔ 16 ia, ɛn i bin go ɔp to di rank fɔ bi liɔtɛnant kɔlɔnɛl, bifo i rigɛn insay 1991 fɔ bigin fɔ du pɔlitikal wok na Sɛnt Pitasbɔg. I bin muf go na Mɔsko insay 1996 fɔ jɔyn di administreshɔn fɔ Prɛsidɛnt Bɔris Yeltsin. I bin wok fɔ shɔt tɛm as dairekta fɔ di Fɛdaral Sikyuriti Savis (FSB) ɛn sɛktri fɔ di Sikyuriti Kaɔnsil, bifo dɛn pik am fɔ bi praymɛnt minista insay Ɔgɔst 1999. Afta we Yeltsin bin rigɛn, Putin bin bi aktin prɛsidɛnt ɛn, i nɔ rich 4 mɔnt afta dat, dɛn bin pik am ɔtrɛyt to in fɔs tɛm as prɛsidɛnt. Dɛn bin ri-ilɛkt am bak insay 2004. As di kɔnstityushɔn se i bin limited to tu kɔnsɛkutiv tɛm as prɛsidɛnt da tɛm de, Putin bin wok as praymɛnt minista bak frɔm 2008 to 2012 ɔnda Dmitry Medvedev. I bin kam bak to di prɛsidɛnshi insay 2012 insay wan ilɛkshɔn we dɛn bin dɔn ambɔg wit alɛgshɔn fɔ frod ɛn protest ɛn dɛn bin ri-ilɛkt am insay 2018. Insay Epril 2021, afta wan rifrendum, i bin sayn insay lɔ kɔnstityushɔn amɛndmɛnt dɛn we inklud wan we go alaw am fɔ rɔn fɔ ri-ilɛkshɔn tu tɛm mɔ, pɔtnɛshɛl fɔ ɛkstɛnd in prɛsidɛnshi to 2036.
